, as well as inner, active, and casual wear for men and women. The company also generates solar power with an installed capacity of 17 MW and wind power with 5 MW, as well as thermal power. It sells its products under the C9 Air wear, Sangam Suiting, and Sangam Denim brands. The company also exports its products. Sangam (India) Limited was incorporated in 1984 and is headquartered in Bhilwara, India."}}